# Frontend (payer web)

## Scope

Public payer flow only — **no JWT, no payee auth**. Payee app is Flutter.

## Structure

- App Router: `frontend/app/`
- Dynamic pay link: `app/[code]/page.tsx`
- Yapily callback: `app/[code]/callback/page.tsx`
- API helpers: `frontend/lib/api.ts`

## Env

- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` → backend `/v1` (default `http://localhost:3001/v1`)

## Patterns

- Server Components for initial link fetch (`GET /pay/:code`)
- Client component for pay button (`POST /pay/:code/initiate` → redirect)
- Types from `@payspin/shared-types` — do not duplicate DTOs

## Dev

```bash
pnpm --filter @payspin/frontend dev   # port 3000
# or: ./scripts/dev/payspin-dev start --web
```

## Production

Deploy separately from API (Vercel or extend prod compose). Set `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` to public API HTTPS URL.
